Class HealthMetric

java.lang.Object
com.example.cab222a.model.core.IdentifiedObject
com.example.cab222a.model.core.NamedObject
com.example.cab222a.model.resist_train.HealthMetric
public class HealthMetric extends NamedObject
Represents the class and information about the Fitness and Health metrics of the user. This includes the userID, metric type, measurement and date recorded. Used to track various metrics such as Weight, BMI, Steps, etc.
